<HL>
   Litton Gets McDonnell Contract
</HL>
<DATE>
07/31/90
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE B7
</SO>
<CO>
   LIT MD
</CO>
<LP>
   BEVERLY HILLS, Calif. -- Litton Industries Inc. said it
received a two-year contract from St. Louis-based McDonnell
Douglas Corp. to develop sensor technology for a fiber-optic
flight-control system for advanced aircraft.
   The companies didn't disclose the amount of the contract.
